OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCovid: Schools asked to    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftest on-site after         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FChristmas                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Secondary schools in England have been 
OL,6, asked to prepare to test pupils on-site
OL,7, after Christmas.                       
OL,9,FOn Friday, the Department for Education
OL,10,Ftold schools that testing pupils upon  
OL,11,Ftheir return in January "will help     
OL,12,Freduce transmission after a period of  
OL,13,Fsocial mixing" during the holidays.    
OL,15,FThe Association of School and College  
OL,16,FLeaders (ASCL) said the DfE's plans    
OL,17,Fwere "not reasonable".                 
OL,19,FJulie McCulloch, director of policy at 
OL,20,FASCL, criticised the "short timeframe".
